---
layout: base.njk
title: Reference
permalink: /tooling/reference/
navSlug: tooling-reference
parentSlug: tooling
subtitle: "MCP tools, template catalog, REST API, and source documentation."
---

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">MCP</div>
    <h2>Tools ({{ tooling.totalTools }})</h2>

    {% for group in tooling.toolGroups %}
    <h3>{{ group.label }} <span class="tooling-note">— {{ group.note }}</span></h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Tool</th><th>Description</th><th>Transport</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for tool in group.tools %}
        <tr>
          <td><code>{{ tool.name }}</code></td>
          <td>{{ tool.description }}</td>
          <td class="tooling-transports">
            {% for t in tool.transports %}
            <span class="transport-badge transport-{{ t }}">{{ t }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Templates</div>
    <h2>Template Catalog ({{ tooling.totalTemplates }})</h2>
    <p style="font-size:14px; color:var(--color-body); margin-bottom:16px;">Auto-generated from <code>templates.meta.ts</code> + a scan of each template's <code>.html</code>. Pass the key to <code>render_template</code>. Visual previews live on <a href="{{ '/documents/' | url }}">Documents</a>, <a href="{{ '/graphics/' | url }}">Graphics</a>, and <a href="{{ '/presentations/' | url }}">Presentations</a>.</p>

    <div class="param-filter">
      <input type="text" id="paramFilter" placeholder="Filter by template key, param, or tag…" oninput="filterParams(this.value)">
    </div>

    <table class="ref-templates-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Template key</th>
          <th>Out</th>
          <th>Size / Format</th>
          <th>Parameters</th>
          <th>Tags</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for tmpl in tooling.allTemplates %}
        <tr class="ref-tmpl-row" data-search="{{ tmpl.key }} {{ tmpl.tags | join(' ') }} {% for p in tmpl.params %}{{ p.name }} {% endfor %}">
          <td>
            <code class="tooling-tmpl-key">{{ tmpl.key }}</code>
            <p class="ref-tmpl-desc">{{ tmpl.description }}</p>
          </td>
          <td><span class="output-badge output-{{ tmpl.output }}">{{ tmpl.output | upper }}</span></td>
          <td class="ref-tmpl-dims">{{ tmpl.dims }}</td>
          <td class="ref-tmpl-params">
            {% if tmpl.params.length %}
              {% for p in tmpl.params %}
              <div class="ref-param">
                <code class="param-name">{{ p.name }}</code>
                <code class="param-type">{{ p.type }}</code>
                {% if p.required %}<span class="param-required">required</span>{% endif %}
                {% if not p.documented %}<span class="param-flag flag-undocumented">undocumented</span>{% endif %}
                {% if p.documented and not p.used %}<span class="param-flag flag-unused">unused</span>{% endif %}
              </div>
              {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
              <span class="params-empty">—</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
          <td class="ref-tmpl-tags">
            {% for t in tmpl.tags %}<span class="tag-chip">{{ t }}</span>{% endfor %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <script>
      function filterParams(q) {
        q = q.trim().toLowerCase();
        document.querySelectorAll('.ref-tmpl-row').forEach(r => {
          r.style.display = !q || r.dataset.search.toLowerCase().includes(q) ? '' : 'none';
        });
      }
    </script>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">HTTP Transport</div>
    <h2>REST API</h2>
    <p style="font-size:14px; color:var(--color-body); margin-bottom:24px;">Base URL: <code>https://mcp.escapevelocity.consulting</code></p>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Method</th><th>Path</th><th>Auth</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for route in tooling.routes %}
        <tr>
          <td><span class="method-badge method-{{ route.method | lower }}">{{ route.method }}</span></td>
          <td><code>{{ route.path }}</code></td>
          <td><span class="auth-tag">{{ route.auth }}</span></td>
          <td>{{ route.purpose }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <h3>Reference</h3>
    <ul class="links-list">
      <li><a href="https://github.com/Escape-Velocity-Consulting/brand/blob/main/BRAND_SPEC.md" target="_blank">BRAND_SPEC.md</a> — Canonical brand specification (source of truth)</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/Escape-Velocity-Consulting/brand/blob/main/docs/mcp-server.md" target="_blank">docs/mcp-server.md</a> — Full MCP server reference (routes, auth, env vars, architecture)</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/Escape-Velocity-Consulting/brand/blob/main/docs/README.md" target="_blank">docs/</a> — Operational documentation (architecture, rules, MCP, publishing, templates, troubleshooting, glossary)</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/Escape-Velocity-Consulting/brand/blob/main/templates.meta.ts" target="_blank">templates.meta.ts</a> — Template registry source (descriptions, dims, required vars)</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/Escape-Velocity-Consulting/brand/blob/main/docs/publishing.md" target="_blank">docs/publishing.md</a> — Publish / unpublish flow and bundle abstraction</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/Escape-Velocity-Consulting/brand/blob/main/BRAND_SKILL.md" target="_blank">BRAND_SKILL.md</a> — Agent cheatsheet for brand system (token table + CSS vars + layout patterns)</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/Escape-Velocity-Consulting/brand/blob/main/tokens.ts" target="_blank">tokens.ts</a> — Token source of truth (colors, fonts, spacing)</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/Escape-Velocity-Consulting/brand/blob/main/tokens.css" target="_blank">tokens.css</a> — Generated CSS custom properties</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/Escape-Velocity-Consulting/brand/blob/main/skill/escape-velocity-brand/SKILL.md" target="_blank">skill/SKILL.md</a> — Deployed skill source (template catalog + routing map)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
